CSEM_Api_Key_Description: Photo DNA Api Service Subscription Key (this app is only active with valid api key)
CSEM_Quarantine_Target_Channel_Descripti: Channel to move CSEM quarantined images to. Be sure to create this channel as documented.
CSEM_Limit_Analysis_To_Channels_Csv_Labe: Limit image analysis to specified channels
CSEM_Limit_Analysis_To_Channels_Csv_Desc: A comma separated values list of channels (e.g. "channelA,channelB") to limit image upload analysis to, all channels if empty
CSEM_Enable_Automated_Report_Description: Automatically report matching images to NCMEC
CSEM_NCMEC_OrgName_Description: The organization name to report violations under
CSEM_NCMEC_ReporterName_Description: The reporter name to report violations under
CSEM_NCMEC_ReporterEmail_Description: The email address to report violations under
CSEM_NCMEC_TestMode_Description: Report violations to the NCMEC test end point
CSEM_NCMEC_User_Description: The username used for the NCMEC cybertip API
CSEM_NCMEC_Password_Description: The password used for the NCMEC cybertip API
